bookTitle: Whatever Gets You Through the Night (The True Lives Of The Fabulous Killjoys, #1)
bookAuthors: Gerard Way, Shaun Simon, Becky Cloonan
Plot: Once upon a time there was a little girl much beloved by a team of heroes called the Killjoys. They swore to protect her. And then a bloody battle broke out between the evil empire of Battery City and these rebels of the Desert. The Killjoys died. The girl lived.
